Data Cloud
Reference unstructured data in Data Cloud by using unstructured data lake objects (UDLOs) to map external blob store files.
Consume unstructured data through unstructured data model objects (UDMOs).
Store chunked object fields and generated vector embeddings using chunk data model objects (CDMO) and vector data model objects (VDMO).

New and Changed Data Model Objects

New and changed data model objects (DMOs) include:

* Search Results DMO
* Search Queries DMO
* Search Interactions DMO
